1d483152-ba80-4663-92fa-ea30fe0be830.title: Professor Oddenstein
1d483152-ba80-4663-92fa-ea30fe0be830.text: Be careful in here, there's lots of dangerous equipment.

options.text: I'm looking for a guy called Ernest.

00221f5f-2438-4e62-a59e-bb84381b0a28.title: Professor Oddenstein
00221f5f-2438-4e62-a59e-bb84381b0a28.text:
No, I'm just one of the tenants. It belongs to the count
who lives in the basement.

9f912ea6-9a0d-4c9e-aed4-369d87de80eb.title: Professor Oddenstein
9f912ea6-9a0d-4c9e-aed4-369d87de80eb.text:
Nothing at the moment... It's broken. It's meant to be
a transmutation machine.

93f8fcc6-79f4-4baf-8a69-d01d78bb8a57.title: Professor Oddenstein
93f8fcc6-79f4-4baf-8a69-d01d78bb8a57.text:
It has also spent time as a time travel machine, and a
dramatic lightning generator, and a thing for generating
monsters.

d45037c7-1c04-43f6-8cf0-91c4b70d0f6c.title: <player>
d45037c7-1c04-43f6-8cf0-91c4b70d0f6c.text: I'm looking for a guy called Ernest.

4394f22c-dd68-46f1-9ad2-a8b34dfca214.title: Professor Oddenstein
4394f22c-dd68-46f1-9ad2-a8b34dfca214.text:
Ah Ernest, top notch bloke. He's helping me with my
experiments.

eadb9bc8-5d19-4231-9c5c-bf1c17222c68.title: <player>
eadb9bc8-5d19-4231-9c5c-bf1c17222c68.text: So you know where he is then?

f369d14b-474c-4db6-9943-a45a505c8307.title: <player>
f369d14b-474c-4db6-9943-a45a505c8307.text: Ernest is a chicken...? Are you sure?

5285a445-b987-4129-b747-3dde87c46343.title: Professor Oddenstein
5285a445-b987-4129-b747-3dde87c46343.text:
Oh, he isn't normally a chicken, or at least he wasn't
until he helped me test my pouletmorph machine.

072f4ca0-ef36-492a-be5f-d7b3ca57948e.title: Professor Oddenstein
072f4ca0-ef36-492a-be5f-d7b3ca57948e.text:
It was originally going to be called a transmutation
machine. But after testing pouletmorph seems more
appropriate.

options.text: I'm glad Veronica didn't actually get engaged to a chicken.

8c089b99-7f8c-4e61-9233-bed8ee2a3d65.title: <player>
8c089b99-7f8c-4e61-9233-bed8ee2a3d65.text:
I'm glad Veronica didn't actually get engaged to a
chicken.

b11cdc4d-058d-4d6f-a0b9-86eec2310498.title: <player>
b11cdc4d-058d-4d6f-a0b9-86eec2310498.text:
Ernest's fiancee. She probably doesn't want to marry a
chicken.

7c01c114-5188-4f9b-aa24-3cc75786292e.title: Professor Oddenstein
7c01c114-5188-4f9b-aa24-3cc75786292e.text: Ooh I dunno. She could have free eggs for breakfast.

3c99b5fc-44b9-41cc-9914-564deba2ab5a.title: <player>
3c99b5fc-44b9-41cc-9914-564deba2ab5a.text: I think you'd better change him back.

cf84a8b2-1be0-4a6a-b279-1707ec59f439.title: Professor Oddenstein
cf84a8b2-1be0-4a6a-b279-1707ec59f439.text:
My machine is broken, and the house gremlins have
run off with some vital bits.

bbab8ce9-58cb-48ae-8d79-03cfb1f8ed12.title: <player>
bbab8ce9-58cb-48ae-8d79-03cfb1f8ed12.text: Well I can look for them.

365bb922-f229-41f4-8849-532204d38171.title: Professor Oddenstein
365bb922-f229-41f4-8849-532204d38171.text:
That would be a help. They'll be somewhere in the
manor house or its grounds, the gremlins never get
further than the entrance gate.

aef41587-1b8f-48d2-aa70-8b23d36fa489.title: Professor Oddenstein
aef41587-1b8f-48d2-aa70-8b23d36fa489.text:
I'm missing the pressure gauge and a rubber tube.
They've also taken my oil can, which I'm going to need
to get this thing started again.

68201741-10bc-4bf2-95c9-a6fce75740db.title: <player>
68201741-10bc-4bf2-95c9-a6fce75740db.text: I'm afraid I don't have them all yet!

a289dc31-30e1-45ba-bf9d-83bc69f46529.title: Professor Oddenstein
a289dc31-30e1-45ba-bf9d-83bc69f46529.text:
I need a rubber tube, a pressure gauge and a can of
oil. Then your friend can stop being a chicken.

40d77977-4bc3-4d06-9c48-ef08b0f9ad12.title: Professor Oddenstein
40d77977-4bc3-4d06-9c48-ef08b0f9ad12.text: Be careful in here, there's lots of dangerous equipment.

2137f610-1587-44bb-a6d0-5e911f79a139.title: Professor Oddenstein
2137f610-1587-44bb-a6d0-5e911f79a139.text:
No, I'm just one of the tenants. It belongs to the count
who lives in the basement.

8b1459c4-ba50-4d03-89d9-e788380d4ba0.title: Professor Oddenstein
8b1459c4-ba50-4d03-89d9-e788380d4ba0.text:
Nothing at the moment... It's broken. It's meant to be
a transmutation machine.

b1c65b61-b7a7-4657-9470-9b7df5b7d69f.title: Professor Oddenstein
b1c65b61-b7a7-4657-9470-9b7df5b7d69f.text:
It has also spent time as a time travel machine, and a
dramatic lightning generator, and a thing for generating
monsters.
